# Fixture trees mirror a representative customer install. The pre-modular fixture
# includes a `.env` whose values are all the literal `REDACTED-FIXTURE-VALUE`; the
# root `.gitignore` ignores `.env` everywhere by default, so this negation makes the
# fixture override explicit. Reviewers can read why a `.env` is tracked here without
# inspecting git's force-add history. Scoped to the one tracked fixture file so a
# future `.env` accidentally dropped elsewhere under this tree stays ignored.
!pre-modular-0.1.x/.env
